CMU Sphinx
---------------------------

CMU Sphinx toolkit has a number of packages for different tasks and applications. 
It's sometimes confusing what to choose. To cleanup, here is the list

	Pocketsphinx - recognizer library written in C.
	Sphinxtrain - acoustic model training tools
	Sphinxbase - support library required by Pocketsphinx and Sphinxtrain
	Sphinx4 - adjustable, modifiable recognizer written in Java
	CMUclmtk - language model tools

Reference:
	http://cmusphinx.sourceforge.net/wiki/download/

